data.text: @HollywoodLife I spoke w someone who worked in Law Enforcement several months ago who said "Husbands cant help their wives with phone calls, People cannot represent themselves Pro Se, & more"; It 'Pays to be 'informed'.

@HollywoodLife Life:  Things that may come your way 1) An aggressive Divorce 2) A Criminal Allegation 3) A Civil Tort Claim 4) More ; And if someone doesn't know how the system works they cld feel like their world spinning OOC.
